### MCP Server Test Requests
### Используйте этот файл в IntelliJ IDEA HTTP Client или VS Code REST Client

### 1. Проверка доступности сервера (GET)
GET http://localhost:8080/health
Accept: application/json

###

### 2. Информация о MCP endpoint (GET)
GET http://localhost:8080/mcp
Accept: text/plain

###

### 3. Инициализация MCP соединения
POST http://localhost:8080/mcp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": 1,
  "method": "initialize",
  "params": {
    "protocolVersion": "2024-11-05",
    "capabilities": {},
    "clientInfo": {
      "name": "test-client",
      "version": "1.0.0"
    }
  }
}

###

### 4. Получить список доступных инструментов
POST http://localhost:8080/mcp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": 2,
  "method": "tools/list"
}

###

### 5. Вызвать инструмент echo
POST http://localhost:8080/mcp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": 3,
  "method": "tools/call",
  "params": {
    "name": "echo",
    "arguments": {
      "text": "Hello, MCP!"
    }
  }
}

###

### 6. Вызвать инструмент get_current_time
POST http://localhost:8080/mcp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": 4,
  "method": "tools/call",
  "params": {
    "name": "get_current_time"
  }
}

###

### 7. Вызвать инструмент calculate
POST http://localhost:8080/mcp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": 5,
  "method": "tools/call",
  "params": {
    "name": "calculate",
    "arguments": {
      "expression": "2 + 2 * 3"
    }
  }
}

###

### 8. Вызвать инструмент yandex_tracker - подсчет открытых задач
POST http://localhost:8080/mcp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": 6,
  "method": "tools/call",
  "params": {
    "name": "yandex_tracker",
    "arguments": {
      "action": "count_open_tasks",
      "queue": "TEST"
    }
  }
}

###

### 9. Вызвать инструмент yandex_tracker - получить список открытых задач
POST http://localhost:8080/mcp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": 7,
  "method": "tools/call",
  "params": {
    "name": "yandex_tracker",
    "arguments": {
      "action": "get_open_tasks",
      "queue": "TEST"
    }
  }
}

###

### 10. Вызвать инструмент yandex_tracker - получить информацию о задаче
POST http://localhost:8080/mcp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": 8,
  "method": "tools/call",
  "params": {
    "name": "yandex_tracker",
    "arguments": {
      "action": "get_task",
      "task_id": "TEST-1",
      "queue": "TEST"
    }
  }
}

###

### 11. Получить список ресурсов
POST http://localhost:8080/mcp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": 9,
  "method": "resources/list"
}

###

### 12. Прочитать ресурс
POST http://localhost:8080/mcp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": 10,
  "method": "resources/read",
  "params": {
    "uri": "file:///example.txt"
  }
}

###


